Invaders Game - Built using Godot Game Engine


To run the project you must follow these steps:

1) install Mono environment

	Ubuntu/Debian one line command:
		sudo apt-get update & sudo apt-get install mono-devel

2) set up godot game engine by one of these methods:
	
	--> compile the source code avaiable at: /invaders/libs-godot/ following the guide 
	avaiable at: http://docs.godotengine.org/en/3.0/development/compiling/compiling_with_mono.html

	--> download the pre-compile version with C# support at: https://godotengine.org/download/linux

3) open the project in /invaders/game


For more information about the game-engine, check: http://docs.godotengine.org/en/3.0/index.html
